    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一段探索恶魔与巫女信仰历史的纪录片之旅，融入现代视角。以自己的节奏沉浸在中世纪的黑暗中，让路西法成为你的向导。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1066740/extras/43bbca2c3e30f7c96de75709709aa9b9.avif?t=1748878801\" width=610 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏以故事和氛围为核心，你不会在这里遇到困难的选择、动作场景或物品管理；移动仅限于随着剧情进展而在各个地点之间穿梭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1066740/extras/c9dd46a99f5245cad939ee0be2aaede9.avif?t=1748878801\" width=610 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从不同时间和地点的多种视角探索黑魔法的复杂信仰。解开数百年来隐藏的神秘知识，追溯恐惧和迷恋在各文化中的演变。沉浸在丰富的历史和地理背景中，每一个背景都提供了对黑暗艺术世界独特的见解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1066740/extras/58ed29ac6c79a9654f9b30aad9c64c0e.avif?t=1748878801\" width=610 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进一个紧张的故事，揭示亵渎神明的严重后果以及对神罚的深刻恐惧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1066740/extras/d53d2492d8279934db4656d48bbda138.avif?t=1748878801\" width=610 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你对这一概念感兴趣，可以查看我们免费改编的H. P. 洛夫克拉夫特的短篇小说《达贡》。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
